Prgms for USP Lab-1
 
P1a. Experiment with set user bit.
    create your executable and data file in /tmp so that others can also
    access.
    (For user1)
     a) open a file (x.dat/txt) for appending.
     b) Read a String
     c) Append to the file
     d) Close the file
 
Requirement:-
    a) remove write permission for others
    b) ask user2 to execute the program
    c) add set user bit  ( Change permission of program)
    d) ask user2 to run the program
 
