P1b.Mimic ls-l command using stat system call Or Simulate stat command
 
struct stat s ;
 
stat("filename", &s);
 
a) s.st_inode// get inode number
b)s.st_node//get node
c)s.st_size// get size
d)s.st_nlink//get link number
 
requirement : display the following:-
a) file name
b)file type
c)file permission
d)size
e)inode #
f) timestamp 
